{"tid":517645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[What a tackle]市民見警察追捕 伸腳絆倒疑犯立功","createTime":"2018-01-02T13:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T04:06:41.000Z","uid":28366,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0083aee2919ec88c616a7c085679ca0cc7b4efcb","tid":517645,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/213346_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F213346_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=00b2b577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國赫特福德郡（Hertford）一名28歲女子在平安夜外出消遣時，目睹警方正追捕一名男子，她於是見義勇為「出」腳將對方絆倒，成功助警方將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，一班男子涉嫌恐嚇酒吧職員，警方截停一輛汽車調查時一名男子逃走，一名女警欲拘捕他但他推開她逃走。從影片看到，23歲男子卡德曼（Aaron Cadman）正嘗試擺脫警員追捕，但28歲女子鮑爾（Kelly Ball）就趁機走上前再伸腳絆倒對方，令他最後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n鮑爾坦言：「我不知道為甚麼這樣做，但就這樣把腳伸出來了，他跑得很快，之後就被絆倒。」事後她腳瘀了一片，幸沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n警方事亦讚揚她的英勇行為，更表揚她說：「她的見義勇為讓我們的警員捉住疑犯，並迅速將他拘捕。」卡德曼被控藏有管有藥物、襲警和醉酒及行為不檢罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180102/57651749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57651749&d=YEKEzsKXkJ7zDZmxM1dhX%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=8f5d5258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57651749&h=2416fb91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180102/57651749</a>"},{"pid":"7fe095b2bd5a1ad3392442091e84327e7bed81f3","tid":517645,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec808383884b3a47fde62b8025e054c97b933667","tid":517645,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T13: